												<a class="dest-link" href="https://greatcanadiantravel.com/destination/scandinavia/">
							<div class="background"></div>
							<div class="title">Scandinavia</div>
							<div class="description">The three countries of Norway, Sweden and Denmark traditionally make up Scandinavia. Some also include Finland in the grouping, based on geologic and economic grounds. Whatever countries you call Scandinavia, we call them all fabulous!</div>
													</a>
					<div class="ui-resizable-handle ui-resizable-se ui-icon ui-icon-gripsmall-diagonal-se" style="z-index: 90; display: none;"></div></div>
