							<div class="background"></div>
							<div class="title">Scotland</div>
							<div class="description">Tap your toes to the skirl of the pipes, sip whisky and soak in the history of the highland clans in bonnie Scotland. </div>
													</a>
					<div class="ui-resizable-handle ui-resizable-se ui-icon ui-icon-gripsmall-diagonal-se" style="z-index: 90; display: none;"></div></div>
